  "abstract": "The Board is adopting an interim final rule amending Regulation Z, which implements the Truth in Lending Act, to establish uniform standards for the electronic delivery of disclosures required by the act and regulation. The rule provides guidance on the timing and delivery of electronic disclosures to ensure consumers have adequate opportunity to access and retain cost information when shopping for credit or before becoming obligated for an extension of credit. (Similar rules are being adopted u",
